{
  "Feature Spec Template": {
    "prefix": "spec-feature",
    "scope": "markdown",
    "description": "Scaffold a feature specification for the GITHUB_skills framework",
    "body": [
      "---",
      "spec_id: ${1:feature-id}",
      "title: ${2:Feature Title}",
      "type: feature",
      "status: draft",
      "author: ${3:your-name}",
      "created: ${CURRENT_YEAR}-${CURRENT_MONTH}-${CURRENT_DATE}",
      "approved_by: \"\"",
      "approved_date: \"\"",
      "---",
      "",
      "# Feature: ${2:Feature Title}",
      "",
      "## Problem Statement",
      "${4:Describe the problem this feature solves and the user pain point.}",
      "",
      "## Proposed Solution",
      "${5:High-level description of the solution.}",
      "",
      "## Acceptance Criteria",
      "- [ ] ${6:First criterion}",
      "- [ ] ${7:Second criterion}",
      "- [ ] ${8:Third criterion}",
      "",
      "## Out of Scope",
      "- ${9:What is explicitly NOT included in this feature.}",
      "",
      "## Open Questions",
      "- ${10:Any unresolved questions or decisions needed.}",
      ""
    ]
  },
  "Bug Spec Template": {
    "prefix": "spec-bug",
    "scope": "markdown",
    "description": "Scaffold a bug specification for the GITHUB_skills framework",
    "body": [
      "---",
      "spec_id: ${1:bug-id}",
      "title: ${2:Bug Title}",
      "type: bugfix",
      "status: draft",
      "author: ${3:your-name}",
      "created: ${CURRENT_YEAR}-${CURRENT_MONTH}-${CURRENT_DATE}",
      "severity: ${4|critical,high,medium,low|}",
      "approved_by: \"\"",
      "approved_date: \"\"",
      "---",
      "",
      "# Bug: ${2:Bug Title}",
      "",
      "## Summary",
      "${5:One-line description of the bug.}",
      "",
      "## Steps to Reproduce",
      "1. ${6:Step one}",
      "2. ${7:Step two}",
      "3. ${8:Step three}",
      "",
      "## Expected Behaviour",
      "${9:What should happen.}",
      "",
      "## Actual Behaviour",
      "${10:What is actually happening.}",
      "",
      "## Root Cause Hypothesis",
      "${11:Suspected cause of the bug, if known.}",
      "",
      "## Acceptance Criteria",
      "- [ ] ${12:The bug is no longer reproducible.}",
      "- [ ] ${13:A regression test has been added.}",
      ""
    ]
  },
  "Spike Spec Template": {
    "prefix": "spec-spike",
    "scope": "markdown",
    "description": "Scaffold a spike/research spec for the GITHUB_skills framework",
    "body": [
      "---",
      "spec_id: ${1:spike-id}",
      "title: ${2:Spike Title}",
      "type: spike",
      "status: draft",
      "author: ${3:your-name}",
      "created: ${CURRENT_YEAR}-${CURRENT_MONTH}-${CURRENT_DATE}",
      "timebox: ${4:2 days}",
      "approved_by: \"\"",
      "approved_date: \"\"",
      "---",
      "",
      "# Spike: ${2:Spike Title}",
      "",
      "## Goal",
      "${5:What question does this spike answer?}",
      "",
      "## Motivation",
      "${6:Why is this investigation needed? What decision does it unblock?}",
      "",
      "## Deliverables",
      "- [ ] ${7:A recommendation document in .copilot/artifact/<spike-id>/research/}",
      "- [ ] ${8:A proof-of-concept or prototype (if applicable)}",
      "",
      "## Timebox",
      "This spike is **timebox to ${4:2 days}**. If no conclusion is reached, escalate.",
      ""
    ]
  },
  "Plan Template": {
    "prefix": "plan-template",
    "scope": "markdown",
    "description": "Scaffold an implementation plan for the GITHUB_skills framework",
    "body": [
      "## Plan: ${1:Feature Title (2-10 words)}",
      "**ID**: ${2:feature/bug ID}",
      "**Spec**: `.copilot/spec/${2:spec-id}.md`",
      "**Research**: `.copilot/artifact/${2:spec-id}/research/`",
      "",
      "---",
      "",
      "## Implementation Steps",
      "",
      "### Step 1: ${3:First Step}",
      "- **File**: `${4:path/to/file.ts}`",
      "- **Action**: ${5:Create / Modify}",
      "- **Details**: ${6:What to implement in this file}",
      "",
      "### Step 2: ${7:Second Step}",
      "- **File**: `${8:path/to/file.ts}`",
      "- **Action**: ${9:Create / Modify}",
      "- **Details**: ${10:What to implement in this file}",
      "",
      "## Unit Tests",
      "| Test | File | Coverage Goal |",
      "|------|------|--------------|",
      "| ${11:Test description} | `${12:test/unit/...}` | ${13:happy path, edge cases} |",
      "",
      "## Dependencies",
      "- ${14:Any external packages or services needed}",
      "",
      "## Risks",
      "- ${15:Any known risks or blockers}",
      ""
    ]
  }
}
